      <title>特朗普命令内阁酋长，而不是马斯克的道德，以裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-orders-cabinet-chiefs-not-doge-to-lead-workforce-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他指示内阁秘书使用“手术刀”而不是“斧头”来裁员，这是一项指令，目的是在裁员浪潮中激怒了联邦劳动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-orders-cabinet-chiefs-not-doge-to-lead-workforce-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 19:19:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟支持德国的努力，以减轻国防的放松财政规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/eu-backs-german-push-to-look-at-easing-fiscal-rules-for-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲联盟同意开始就其财政规则进行长期改革进行讨论，以允许成员国从德国进行推动之后，在国防上花费更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/eu-backs-german-push-to-look-at-easing-fiscal-rules-for-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 19:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）称跨性别运动员在女子运动中“深不别一错”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/gavin-newsom-says-trans-athletes-in-women-s-sports-is-deeply-unfair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LGBTQ权利的长期倡导者加利福尼亚州州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）对跨性别运动员在妇女体育运动中的比赛表示关注，对这个问题对民主党的政治分歧采取了更为保守的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/gavin-newsom-says-trans-athletes-in-women-s-sports-is-deeply-unfair</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 19:13:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲的防御风险在几周内没有美国支持的情况下步履蹒跚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-03-06/europe-s-defenses-against-russia-invasion-would-last-weeks-without-trump-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果受到攻击，欧洲的弹药库存可能会在几天之内降低，而饲养将需要数年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-03-06/europe-s-defenses-against-russia-invasion-would-last-weeks-without-trump-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Alphabet在据称的演讲审查中获得了共和党传票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/alphabet-receives-house-republican-subpoena-over-speech-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由共和党领导的众议院司法委员会向Alphabet Inc.及其首席执行官Sundar Pichai进行了传唤，这是对最大科技公司与Biden Administration的关系的持续调查的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/alphabet-receives-house-republican-subpoena-over-speech-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 18:41:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普收紧了对联邦人力资源负责人的控制，使角色政治化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-tightens-control-over-federal-hr-chiefs-politicizing-roles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的政府正在将最高的联邦机构人力资源工作重新分类为政治角色，这扭转了一项长期的政策，让人事首长成为职业政府官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-tightens-control-over-federal-hr-chiefs-politicizing-roles</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 18:12:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bessent说，美国会毫不犹豫地对俄罗斯和伊朗制裁。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-won-t-hesitate-on-russia-and-iran-sanctions-bessent-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）周四表示，如果美国对俄罗斯能源的制裁有助于导致乌克兰战争的停火，那么美国将毫不犹豫地“全力以赴”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-won-t-hesitate-on-russia-and-iran-sanctions-bessent-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 17:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国按乌克兰迅速停战与矿产交易一起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-presses-ukraine-for-quick-ceasefire-to-go-with-minerals-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲官员被告知，唐纳德·特朗普总统希望将拟议的美国 - 乌克兰矿业协议与基辅的要求联系，要求基辅致力于与俄罗斯快速停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-presses-ukraine-for-quick-ceasefire-to-go-with-minerals-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 17:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他将推迟墨西哥在USMCA下的商品关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-likely-to-defer-tariffs-on-goods-services-under-usmca</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他将对属于北美贸易协定的任何商品和服务的新的25％关税免税，称为USMCA，为美国主要贸易伙伴提供缓刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-likely-to-defer-tariffs-on-goods-services-under-usmca</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 15:15:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙可以在5月举行选举，因为总理缺乏盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/portugal-may-hold-an-early-election-in-may-president-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统马塞洛·雷贝洛·德·索萨（Marcelo Rebelo de Sousa）说，如果政府在议会下周在议会上失去信心投票，葡萄牙可能会在5月面临早期选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/portugal-may-hold-an-early-election-in-may-president-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 20:09:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
